Author : Baye-Saliou Falling
Topic : Image processing using a mean filter
Language: Java 

There is a parallel and serial version of the same mean filter. The parallel version uses the ForkJoin Framework. The programs uses the
sliding window technique to filter the image.

How to run the programs :

java Program.java inputImage.jpg outputImage.jpg windowLength 

.....this will produce outputImage.jpg which is filtered. Ensure that inputImage.jpg is in the same directory as Program.java.

Read the comments on the code to understand it better. 

